Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.57,0:00:17.55,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕らは未来を変える力を　夢に見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:36.14,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ノイズの中　聞こえて来た君の泣き声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:47.16,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}笑っていた　僕の弱さを暴いた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:52.92,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君の行く道は　君にしか分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:58.78,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}違う空　追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:07.50,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕等は未来へ向かう勇気を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:13.33,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}欲しがって過去に迷う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:27.91,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君が笑うほんとうの現在へ帰り付くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.57,0:00:17.55,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我们梦想着  改变未来的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:36.14,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}杂音中  传来你的哭泣声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:47.16,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}揭开我  欢笑之下的软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:52.92,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的前路  只有你能决定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:58.78,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}追逐着  不同的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:07.50,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我们渴求着前往未来的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:13.33,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}却为此在过去迷失了方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:27.91,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}直至回到你所微笑着的此时此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.61,0:22:31.14,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}金色の午後は　ママレイドティーとビスケット
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.29,0:22:37.74,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}散らかったトランプで　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.78,0:22:46.34,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}さぁ夢の続きを占いましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.16,0:22:54.82,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いくつのドア　開くのでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.19,0:23:02.77,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}…サガシモノ　何処ニアル？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:06.84,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君だけを見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.95,0:23:11.00,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君だけ追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.10,0:23:18.36,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}気づけば　私は迷子で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:26.73,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}秘密の暗号　君だけに送ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.14,0:23:29.90,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}はやく見つけて　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.99,0:23:35.55,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「私はここだよ。」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.61,0:22:31.14,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}金色的午后  品尝着柚子茶和饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.29,0:22:37.74,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}收起散落一地的纸牌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.78,0:22:46.34,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}来  占卜梦境的后续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.16,0:22:54.82,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}会打开多少扇大门呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.19,0:23:02.77,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}…寻找的东西  究竟在何处？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:06.84,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只注视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.95,0:23:11.00,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只追逐着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.10,0:23:18.36,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这才发现我迷了路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:26.73,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只向你送去  秘密的暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.14,0:23:29.90,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}快点找到我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.99,0:23:35.55,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「我在这里哦。」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//ED
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了将来你能陪在艾莉丝身边  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该要知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.59,0:01:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那时为止  她还是个人类
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.57,0:02:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百年前在这里被杀死的那时为止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.62,0:02:06.62,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了某人的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.24,0:02:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝…死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一百年前的…这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为人类…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被某个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:49.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被杀了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.51,0:03:11.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被杀了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.65,0:03:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了  奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转动了吗…		
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹君的刻印的时针…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.07,0:04:44.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝…在叫我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  你对我来说是特别的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我深陷痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是有人伤害我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时  你要来帮我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:33.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.44,0:05:37.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦的力量被抑制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,染血黑兔正在暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.17,0:05:43.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制不住它了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  麻烦了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.98,0:05:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个场景对奥兹的打击好像太大了些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？你是说这些都是奥兹做的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.07,0:05:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:06:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能  奥兹怎么可能做得到那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.58,0:06:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,染血黑兔力量的源头是封印在奥兹的身体里的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:11.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…现在的情况并不乐观呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.02,0:06:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界如果毁灭的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被封在记忆中的艾莉丝和奥兹  还有你  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…基尔巴特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不能因为你受了伤  而继续让你在这休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:39.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请阻止奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.28,0:06:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去阻止你敬爱的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这个力气动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑脸猫已经没时间跟你耗下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷淡啊  再陪我玩玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:15.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑脸猫要去杀了那个金发的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:19.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙现在正在破坏这个空间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金发？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.88,0:07:25.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说现在使用力量的人是奥兹君吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,染血黑兔的力量和我的疯狂帽商一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:55.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…真的是奥兹他…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.91,0:08:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  和染血黑兔  还有鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑脸猫要杀光你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑脸猫只是为了那孩子才在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:16.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了她  杀光你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明是只猫  说的话怎么跟某只阴沟老鼠一样	
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你一件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:29.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最讨厌「为了某人」这种不负责任的借口了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:09:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快阻止染血黑兔的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则你的身体就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.04,0:09:15.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要毁掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要毁掉…  艾莉丝想要忘记的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部  都由我来毁掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.03,0:09:27.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊  奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听…  能听到声音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.48,0:09:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝悲伤的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.98,0:09:39.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.18,0:09:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么让你这么害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:53.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:57.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮你毁掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:10:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让艾莉丝伤心的东西  伤害艾莉丝的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.19,0:10:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部毁掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.82,0:10:09.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  笑一笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我重要的艾莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:21.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好害怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕自己不是人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:27.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕自己和其它灵体不同…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕自己一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:35.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也害怕去了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:38.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何时  我都…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.48,0:10:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比谁都…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更害怕自己这个存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.57,0:10:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:50.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:54.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就毁掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:11:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁掉的话  你就没有必要再痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮你消除的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.62,0:11:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  只要消除掉就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.89,0:11:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮你消除掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:22.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  只要消除掉就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我适可而止！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.13,0:12:06.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:16.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你到这里是来做什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:17.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说给我听  奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来救那笨兔子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来救艾莉丝的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然笑脸猫已经尽力了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:06.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可游戏也快要进入决胜局了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同我的预期  再过一会儿 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝的记忆应该就会来到我们的世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:19.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你这个容易操纵的棋子在  真是帮了我大忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帽商先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…真是的  好讨厌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一使用力量马上就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:39.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是不要乱动比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是你也会消失的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:51.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是赢不了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.57,0:13:55.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微动动脑子就能明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:14:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的疯狂帽商  能否定一切与阿比斯有关联的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让其消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为它是为了消灭灵体而存在的灵体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算那样  笑脸猫也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.57,0:14:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会逃…是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很郑重地带在身上的  这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是制造出这个空间的核心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.53,0:14:39.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百年前的艾莉丝的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实实在在地收下了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.15,0:15:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些…是我做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:04.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.16,0:15:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想让艾莉丝消失
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.79,0:15:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:16.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子是赶上了呢  基尔巴特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是千钧一发  艾莉丝她没事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:47.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是因为奥兹…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.69,0:15:49.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.06,0:16:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.40,0:16:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说不知道自己做了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:21.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…我  差点就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀掉艾莉丝了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:25.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.19,0:16:35.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比谁都害怕自己这个存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.17,0:16:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  我没有想过那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会对艾莉丝怀有的不安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:43.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说那种过份的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.34,0:16:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝…艾莉丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.39,0:16:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不了解身为人类时的艾莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  现在的艾莉丝  我是了解的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:16:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.31,0:17:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然容易生气  喜欢乱踢人  嘴巴也很坏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其实…又善良  又心软
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说了  我明明想就这样睡下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.10,0:17:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会时不时地犯傻  是个令人吃惊的贪吃鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.38,0:17:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贪吃鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非因为是人类  你才是艾莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.84,0:17:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也并非因为是灵体  你才是艾莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是从动作  想法  表情  这一点一滴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:18:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都传达着艾莉丝就是艾莉丝这个事实
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.09,0:18:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会在一旁好好看着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝就是艾莉丝  这样就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.49,0:18:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得太晚了  你这没用的仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那时候的艾莉丝不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.43,0:18:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地活着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.33,0:18:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:19:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是只不老实的猫咪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.29,0:19:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟～  贵安～  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵安你个头啊  都怪你事情才会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.88,0:19:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了知道了  之后再听你抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.05,0:19:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那东西难道是…笑脸猫？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.93,0:19:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  虽说变成这种丑态了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.31,0:19:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是曾经希望变成人  才会有人的形态
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.07,0:19:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然自己舍弃掉自己的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:28.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿比斯的意志真有那么重要么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定是想成为…  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.93,0:19:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能将重要的人守护到底的  唯一的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.46,0:19:44.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝…艾莉丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:49.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你伤心的东西  伤害你的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都由笑脸猫…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:59.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他准备跟我们和这个空间同归于尽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.43,0:20:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快用独角兽逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  独角兽还没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.15,0:20:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷克  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.41,0:20:15.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.89,0:20:20.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑脸猫的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.74,0:20:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独角兽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.64,0:20:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  基尔和布雷克还在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:50.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  夏罗  快阻止独角兽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.02,0:20:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏罗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.68,0:21:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔  布雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  不行  我还有很多事不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝的事  萨布里耶的悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.14,0:21:17.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那家伙到底是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.39,0:21:28.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想什么都没了解就这么结束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们出来到了哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口…好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.33,0:21:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.28,0:21:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥斯卡叔叔？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.86,0:21:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.63,0:21:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,染血黑兔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.88,0:23:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}那么大只的兔子能往哪藏啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.00,0:23:46.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}你果然是看到什么了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.80,0:23:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}不要碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.51,0:23:52.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}夏罗大小姐是不是遇上什么不测了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.14,0:23:56.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}真会骗人呢  帽商先生……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.60,0:24:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}他将再次给这片大地带来灾厄！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.23,0:24:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}将萨布里耶的悲剧带来这片大地！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.73,0:24:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  英雄与少年